===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|en-us-basin.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|eɪsən}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[bowl]] for [[washing]], often affixed to a wall.
# {{geography}} An [[area]] of water that [[drain]]s into a [[river]].
# {{geography}} A rock [[formation]] [[scoop]]ed out by water [[erosion]].

